  <Entries>
    <Entry>
      <ID>1</ID>
      <DefaultText>A bald man with a crooked nose gestures in demonstration over the still body of a patient before a small gathering of interested onlookers. Feeling your gaze, he pauses his discussion.

"Have you come to sit in?"</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>2</ID>
      <DefaultText>"Hello again. Can I be of some use to you?"</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>3</ID>
      <DefaultText>"I'd like to know more about the sanitarium."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>4</ID>
      <DefaultText>"What is it you do here?"</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>5</ID>
      <DefaultText>"Farewell."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>7</ID>
      <DefaultText>He gives an eager nod. "It's the mission that attracted me here. The treatment of the disturbed. No one else seems to care about them. Here... they've worked wonders for them."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>8</ID>
      <DefaultText>"Close as we are to the Glanfathan wilds, we get a number of b&#238;a&#373;ac maimings every year. Survivors dealing with complications from exposure. This fellow here is a severe case - his essence is a mere whisper of what it was."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>10</ID>
      <DefaultText>"Has anything unusual or suspicious been happening around here?"</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>11</ID>
      <DefaultText>He shakes his head. "Definitely not up here - we can't be scaring off visitors and potential clients, you know."

His voice becomes quiet. "Downstairs is where the, uh, more esoteric research is done. I'd check with the animancers there."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>12</ID>
      <DefaultText>"Do you know anything about Awakenings?"</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>13</ID>
      <DefaultText>"I'm afraid that's not my area of expertise."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>14</ID>
      <DefaultText>"I've seen people cured of insatiable hungers and uncontrollable urges. I've seen the crippled walk and the dysphoric smile. All within these walls.

"The thought that the duc could put an end to it with a single order, it keeps me up nights."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>15</ID>
      <DefaultText>"I am early in my research, only beginning to understand how they work. But in time, I hope to find a way to protect people from the storm's effects."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
  </Entries>
</StringTableFile>